{"tid":2099897,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"員工家屬確診 將軍澳彩明譚仔停業3天消毒棄貨","createTime":"2020-07-08T15:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T06:11:02.000Z","uid":222970,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e904b9e81218e9da1ad53d045d59c5af314f3c4d","tid":2099897,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uFpdW52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuFpdW52.jpg&h=1adb0f64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n員工家屬確診 將軍澳彩明譚仔停業3天消毒棄貨<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳彩明邨的「譚仔雲南米線」一名員工家屬確診感染武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳彩明邨的「譚仔雲南米線」一名員工家屬確診感染武漢肺炎。譚仔晚上在官方Facebook發表聲明，指該員工在其家屬初感不適時，已沒有上班，至今兩天，但被列為緊密接觸者。公司決定即時關閉該分店，停業3天全面消毒，包括抽風系統；棄置該分店已開封或有機會受污染的食材；該分店其他同事會隔離14天，確定沒有受感染方可上班，以保障客人及員工的健康安全。<br />\n<br />\n公司又指，員工須每天上班前量度體溫，如有不適、發燒或出現其他症狀，須立即離開工作崗位，即時求診及向管理層匯報。至於彩明分店於7月11日（星期六）重新營業，公司會安排其他分店健康良好的員工，暫調至彩明分店。公司強調重視顧客及員工健康，一向有嚴謹員工健康及外遊紀錄申報機制，以及防疫措施。對於有員工家屬確診引致各人不安及不便，公司深感抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200708/MDT7YU7S6WKQYY7VRWYNXJ3ESE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200708%2FMDT7YU7S6WKQYY7VRWYNXJ3ESE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK1R4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=e8ef013d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200708%2FMDT7YU7S6WKQYY7VRWYNXJ3ESE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=e714607e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200708/MDT7YU7S6WKQYY7VRWYNXJ3ESE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https:/